664.text: But, it goes on '_they all returned from him to you_,'

666.text:
Nothing can be clearer than _that_. Then
again--'_before she had this fit_--' you never had fits, my dear, I
think?

670.text: Let the jury consider their verdict,

674.text:
The idea of having the
sentence first!

679.text: You're nothing but a pack of cards!

681.text:
Why, what a long sleep you've
had!

682.text: Oh, I've had such a curious dream!

683.text:
It _was_ a curious
dream, dear, certainly: but now run in to your tea; it's getting late.
